sectionNotes: Restricted to Food Science & Human Nutrition or Food Science or Nutrition major(s) or minor(s).
sectionText: FSHN majors and minors only.  If you get a 'course full' error message and want to be added to a wait list for this class, go to www.fshn.illinois.edu and click on Current Students then Waitlist Information. Wait lists will not open until one week before classes start in January.
